-- Amazon's Kindle still in "investment phase": CEO
-- 
-- Wed May 28, 2008 12:56pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/05/28/us-amazon-idUSN2834358520080528

 

 LOS ANGELES  (Reuters) - Amazon.com Inc's electronic book reader, the Kindle, is still in its investment phase, the Internet retailer's chief executive told CNBC on Wednesday. 

 CEO Jeff Bezos would not reveal how many Kindles the Seattle-based company had sold since its launch in November, but said the price had recently been lowered to $359 from  $399. (Reporting by  Alexandria Sage ; editing by Jeffrey Benkoe)